Utterance.UttText: In bed 23 is Melanie thompson, 34 yrs old under Dr Gray.
She Came in with flu and fever and got it 2 days after an overseas holiday.
She is on oxygen 3 litres per nasal prongs.

Phrase.PhraseText: on oxygen 3 litres per nasal prongs.

Utterance.UttText: She is ambulant and self caring.
